To create a modern, visually striking portfolio website with the specified features, follow this structured implementation:

portfolio-website/
├── dist/               # Bundled files
├── src/
│   ├── ts/             # TypeScript files
│   ├── scss/           # Sass files
│   ├── assets/         # Images, fonts, icons
│   └── index.html
├── webpack.config.js
└── package.json

Enhancements :
Dark/Light Toggle : Persist state with localStorage
Custom Cursor : Create a div with position: fixed and sync with mouse movement
SVG Dividers : Use inline SVGs for decorative section separators
Lazy Loading : Add loading="lazy" to images
Deployment :
Optimize images with tools like TinyPNG
Use Lighthouse for performance audits
Deploy via Netlify/Vercel with CI/CD
This implementation balances performance, accessibility, and visual appeal while leveraging modern web technologies. Adjust animations and layouts based on device capabilities for optimal user experience.
